transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thanks for calling Viagra Clinic speaking. How can I help you?

Speaker 2: Yeah, this is Jimmy Okun. I need to cancel my subscription.

Speaker 1: Okay, one moment. Let me pull up your account.

Speaker 2: Alrighty, Mr. Okun, I do see that you are a VIP with us here.

Speaker 1: Do you mind if I ask why you're cancelling?

Speaker 2: Yeah, because it don't work.

Speaker 1: Oh wow, that is unfortunate, but I'm not sure if you're aware.

Speaker 2: This is like a body chemistry type of medication. It's about the blood flow in your body.

Speaker 1: We do have others that may be a better fit for you that we can send you for free, free of charge.

Speaker 2: No, I just want to cancel it.

Speaker 1: And if it's not working, why would you not want to try something for free?

Speaker 2: Because I don't want to.

Speaker 1: And you do realize you can order this as needed. You don't have to get it automatically or when you're not ready for it.

Speaker 2: You do understand that as well, correct?

Speaker 1: I don't need it.

Speaker 2: Alrighty, well you won't get it, sir. We'll go ahead and cancel you out so you will not be able to reorder with us in the future, okay?

Speaker 1: Alright, thank you.
